<script>
  	async function logLastChat() {
        const chatWindow = document.getElementById('chat-window-messages');
        if (chatWindow) {
            const chatRightMessages = document.querySelectorAll('.chat-right .chat-content');
            const lastChatRightMessage = chatRightMessages[chatRightMessages.length - 1];
            if (lastChatRightMessage) {
                const messageContent = lastChatRightMessage.textContent.trim();
                if (messageContent) {
                    const referrer = document.referrer;

                    let urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
                    let paramsObject = {};
                    const utmParams = {};

                    const utmKeys = ['utm_source', 'utm_medium', 'utm_campaign', 'utm_term', 'utm_content'];

                    urlParams.forEach((value, key) => {
                        paramsObject[key] = value;
                        document.cookie = key + "=" + value;
                    });
                    const urlParamsString = JSON.stringify(paramsObject);

                    utmKeys.forEach(key => {
                        if (urlParams.has(key)) {
                            utmParams[key] = urlParams.get(key);
                        }
                    });

                    const cookie = document.cookie;

                    const url = 'https://contao.ra-cocron.de/jupus/chatbot/log';
                    const data = {
                        message: messageContent,
                        referrer: referrer,
                        url_parameters: urlParamsString,
                        cookie: cookie,
                        is_last: true,
                    };

                    // Add UTM parameters to the data object
                    for (const key in utmParams) {
                        if (utmParams.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
                            data[key] = utmParams[key];
                        }
                    }

                    try {
                        const response = await fetch(url, {
                            method: 'POST',
                            headers: {
                                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                                'Referer': referrer,
                            },
                            body: JSON.stringify(data),
                        });

                        // Check if the request was successful
                        if (response.ok) {
                            // console.log('Message saved successfully:', message);
                        } else {
                            // console.error('Error saving message:', response.status);
                        }
                    } catch (error) {
                        // console.error('Error sending POST request:', error);
                    }
                }

            }
        }
    }

            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({

            });
        });

        {/* appointmentLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_appointment_click"
            });
        }); */}

            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_phone_berlin_click"
            });
        });

        muenchenPhoneLink.addEventListener("click", function () {
            window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            window.dataLayer.push({
                event: "topbar_phone_muenchen_click"
            });
        });

        // Intercept dataLayer pushes

            const originalPush = dataLayer.push;
            dataLayer.push = function () {
                const args = Array.prototype.slice.call(arguments);
                let isBlocked = false;
                args.forEach(async function (obj) {

                            console.log('topbar_appointment_click');

<Script>
  	Async Function Loglastchat() {
        Const Chatwindow = Document.Getelementbyid('Chat-Window-Messages');
        If (Chatwindow) {
            Const Chatrightmessages = Document.Queryselectorall('.Chat-Right .Chat-Content');
            Const Lastchatrightmessage = Chatrightmessages[Chatrightmessages.Length - 1];
            If (Lastchatrightmessage) {
                Const Messagecontent = Lastchatrightmessage.Textcontent.Trim();
                If (Messagecontent) {
                    Const Referrer = Document.Referrer;

                    Let Urlparams = New Urlsearchparams(Window.Location.Search);
                    Let Paramsobject = {};
                    Const Utmparams = {};

                    Const Utmkeys = ['Utm_Source', 'Utm_Medium', 'Utm_Campaign', 'Utm_Term', 'Utm_Content'];

                    Urlparams.Foreach((Value, Key) => {
                        Paramsobject[Key] = Value;
                        Document.Cookie = Key + "=" + Value;
                    });
                    Const Urlparamsstring = Json.Stringify(Paramsobject);

                    Utmkeys.Foreach(Key => {
                        If (Urlparams.Has(Key)) {
                            Utmparams[Key] = Urlparams.Get(Key);
                        }
                    });

                    Const Cookie = Document.Cookie;

                    Const Url = 'Https://Contao.Ra-Cocron.De/Jupus/Chatbot/Log';
                    Const Data = {
                        Message: Messagecontent,
                        Referrer: Referrer,
                        Url_Parameters: Urlparamsstring,
                        Cookie: Cookie,
                        Is_Last: True,
                    };

                    // Add Utm Parameters To The Data Object
                    For (Const Key In Utmparams) {
                        If (Utmparams.Hasownproperty(Key)) {
                            Data[Key] = Utmparams[Key];
                        }
                    }

                    Try {
                        Const Response = Await Fetch(Url, {
                            Method: 'Post',
                            Headers: {
                                'Content-Type': 'Application/Json',
                                'Referer': Referrer,
                            },
                            Body: Json.Stringify(Data),
                        });

                        // Check If The Request Was Successful
                        If (Response.Ok) {
                            // Console.Log('Message Saved Successfully:', Message);
                        } Else {
                            // Console.Error('Error Saving Message:', Response.Status);
                        }
                    } Catch (Error) {
                        // Console.Error('Error Sending Post Request:', Error);
                    }
                }

            }
        }
    }

<script>
  window.addEventListener("load", setUlMargin);
  window.addEventListener("resize", setUlMargin);

  function setUlMargin() {
    const header = document.querySelector("header");
    const ul = document.querySelector(".cr-header__nav-items");

    if (header && ul && window.innerWidth <= 768) {
      const headerHeight = header.offsetHeight;
      ul.style.top = "0";
      ul.style.marginTop = `${headerHeight}px`;
    }
  }
</script>
